title: Photos: Saif’s Daughter Sara Ali Khan Looks Gorgeous At Shahid’s Birthday Bash
text:
Rashmi Daryanani Feb . 20 . 2017 
Shahid Kapoor ‘s Rangoon co-star, Saif Ali Khan , wasn’t present at his birthday bash, as he’s promoting the film in Delhi along with Kangana Ranaut . However, Saif’s daughter, Sara , put in an appearance. The young girl is all set to make her Bollywood debut, and although there were rumours that Saif doesn’t want Karan Johar to launch his daughter, the budding actress was seen posing with him at the party: Sara Ali Khan and Karan Johar Sara Ali Khan and Karan Johar Sara Ali Khan and Karan Johar Sara Ali Khan and Karan Johar ‹ › ‹ › 
It looks like Karan will indeed be launching Sara, as Saif was quoted in a recent interview as saying “it’s Sara’s decision” and he thinks she’s going to debut with Karan. He also went on to say that he was happy she was working with this director, as “he is brilliant with newcomers”. Well, he does have three students to prove it! 2
